om/book/116949/\" title=\"斗破之马气大陆（斗破苍穹之马气大陆）\">斗破之马气大陆（斗破苍穹之马气大陆）</a>\r\n\t\t</h4>\r\n\t\t<div class=\"author\">江南夜色下</div>\r\n\t\t<div class=\"intro\">这里是属于马气的世界，没有花俏艳丽的魔法，有的，仅仅是繁衍到巅峰的马气！ 我是一个废物，正在被好几个斗帝追杀，但是我内心毫无波澜，甚至特么还有点想笑。 因为，我的马儿比他们的马儿跑得快~~~ 小斗者！你给…</div>\r\n\t</div>\r\n</div><div class=\"col-sm-6 col-md-4 book-coverlist\">\r\n\t<a class=\"cover\" href=\"https://www.shenhuazhihou.com/book/105972/\">\r\n\t\t<img class=\"thumbnail\" src=\"https://www.shenhuazhihou.com/d/file/book/94358bc5d157c86b57cd14fea5432eeb.jpg\" data-src=\"\" width=\"120px\" height=\"160px\" alt=\"斗破苍穹前传之药老传奇\">\r\n\t</a>\r\n\t<div class=\"caption\">\r\n\t\t<h4 class=\"name\">\r\n\t\t\t<a href=\"https://www.shenhuazhihou.com/book/105972/\" title=\"斗破苍穹前传之药老传奇\">斗破苍穹前传之药老传奇</a>\r\n\t\t</h4>\r\n\t\t<div class=\"author\">天蚕土豆</div>\r\n\t\t<div class=\"intro\">这里是斗气的世界，强者尊，弱者卑。 药族，远古八族之一，属斗帝血脉，炼药师的朝拜圣地。 药尘，萧炎恩师，从卑微药族到斗气大陆巅峰。…</div>\r\n\t</div>\r\n</div><div class=\"col-sm-6 col-md-4 book-coverlist\">\r\n\t<a class=\"cover\" href=\"https://www.shenhuazhihou.com/book/99748/\">\r\n\t\t<img class=\"thumbnail\" src=\"https://www.shenhuazhihou.com/d/file/book/c11a2aa3cf0a5388ed6f59e2711d398c.jpg\" data-src=\"\" width=\"120px\" height=\"160px\" alt=\"斗破苍穹之万界商城\">\r\n\t</a>\r\n\t<div class=\"caption\">\r\n\t\t<h4 class=\"name\">\r\n\t\t\t<a href=\"https://www.shenhuazhihou.com/book/99748/\" title=\"斗破苍穹之万界商城\">斗破苍穹之万界商城</a>\r\n\t\t</h4>\r\n\t\t<div class=\"author\">梦回夕照</div>\r\n\t\t<div class=\"intro\">新书《诸天万界BOSS聊天群》已发布，求收藏！意外来到斗破苍穹世界的夜時秋拥有一个包涵万物的商城系统，界门开启，一个个位面之骄降临大陆，演绎出震撼人心的画...…</div>\r\n\t</div>\r\n</div><div class=\"col-sm-6 col-md-4 book-coverlist\">\r\n\t<a class=\"cover\" href=\"https://www.shenhuazhihou.com/book/75351/\">\r\n\t\t<img class=\"thumbnail\" src=\"https://www.shenhuazhihou.com/d/file/book/c129b7dc2e9777ebc9f6b1151f5d5c42.jpg\" data-src=\"\" width=\"120px\" height=\"160px\" alt=\"斗破苍穹之冰帝海波东\">\r\n\t</a>\r\n\t<div class=\"caption\">\r\n\t\t<h4 class=\"name\">\r\n\t\t\t<a href=\"https://www.shenhuazhihou.com/book/75351/\" title=\"斗破苍穹之冰帝海波东\">斗破苍穹之冰帝海波东</a>\r\n\t\t</h4>\r\n\t\t<div class=\"author\">作家SesVBA</div>\r\n\t\t<div class=\"intro\">这本书的开头是海波东的一位红颜知己他的小师妹自杀之后，他心灰意冷想要寻求突破的时陷入困境灵魂震荡获得了原著剧情。在这个故事里的海波东会保持跟动漫一样的性格，他会遇到各种奇遇，与原著有着重…</div>\r\n\t</div>\r\n</div><div class=\"col-sm-6 col-md-4 book-coverlist\">\r\n\t<a class=\"cover\" href=\"https://www.shenhuazhihou.com/book/74092/\">\r\n\t\t<img class=\"thumbnail\" src=\"https://www.shenhuazhihou.com/d/file/book/a9624b141eeaa8cff980affeb55edce4.jpg\" data-src=\"\" width=\"120px\" height=\"160px\" alt=\"斗破苍穹之魂天帝\">\r\n\t</a>\r\n\t<div class=\"caption\">\r\n\t\t<h4 class=\"name\">\r\n\t\t\t<a href=\"https://www.shenhuazhihou.com/book/74092/\" title=\"斗破苍穹之魂天帝\">斗破苍穹之魂天帝</a>\r\n\t\t</h4>\r\n\t\t<div class=\"author\">破天行者</div>\r\n\t\t<div class=\"intro\">新书《大齐斩妖师》已发布，故事生动有趣，直接搜书名。双帝之战后，终级大反派魂天帝被同样成为斗帝的萧炎给封印了起来不知过了多少岁月后，在魂天帝灵魂即将消散之际，莫名穿越到了萧炎还是废材时代，事情…</div>\r\n\t</div>\r\n</div><div class=\"col-sm-6 col-md-4 book-coverlist\">\r\n\t<a class=\"cover\" href=\"https://www.shenhuazhihou.com/book/70137/\">\r\n\t\t<img class=\"thumbnail\" src=\"https://www.shenhuazhihou.com/d/file/book/a05a21aec269f2902c58a33f23dd99b8.jpg\" data-src=\"\" width=\"120px\" height=\"160px\" alt=\"斗破苍穹之魔帝萧炎\">\r\n\t</a>\r\n\t<div class=\"caption\">\r\n\t\t<h4 class=\"name\">\r\n\t\t\t<a href=\"https://www.shenhuazhihou.com/book/70137/\" title=\"斗破苍穹之魔帝萧炎\">斗破苍穹之魔帝萧炎</a>\r\n\t\t</h4>\r\n\t\t<div class=\"author\">朽木罢了</div>\r\n\t\t<div class=\"intro\">众叛亲离,孤独一人成为盖世强者的魔怒圣者萧炎,在探寻斗帝之秘时,却穿过了时间之门。原本处于黑化线的他却重生到了正常线的斗气大陆,经历注定不平凡的人生………</div>\r\n\t</div>\r\n</div><div class=\"col-sm-6 col-md-4 book-coverlist\">\r\n\t<a class=\"cover\" href=\"https://www.shenhuazhihou.com/book/68871/\">\r\n\t\t<img class=\"thumbnail\" src=\"https://www.shenhuazhihou.com/d/file/book/c9fdff16274c560779affc5c45a57576.jpg\" data-src=\"\" width=\"120px\" height=\"160px\" alt=\"斗破苍穹之至高真神\">\r\n\t</a>\r\n\t<div class=\"caption\">\r\n\t\t<h4 class=\"name\">\r\n\t\t\t<a href=\"https://www.shenhuazhihou.com/book/68871/\" title=\"斗破苍穹之至高真神\">斗破苍穹之至高真神</a>\r\n\t\t</h4>\r\n\t\t<div class=\"author\">落日精灵</div>\r\n\t\t<div class=\"intro\">大千世界,位面集结,万道争锋,真龙降世,一位突破位面桎梏的炎帝萧炎,降临在这片浩瀚的无尽世界,会演绎怎样的传奇？各方天之至尊层出不穷,追逐那令人向往的主宰之路,探索主宰之上的神之领域。等级制…</div>\r\n\t</div>\r\n</div><div class=\"col-sm-6 col-md-4 book-coverlist\">\r\n\t<a class=\"cover\" href=\"https://www.shenhuazhihou.com/book/48899/\">\r\n\t\t<img class=\"thumbnail\" src=\"https://www.shenhuazhihou.com/d/file/book/67e3acbd597666c939b55b5ffae472a6.jpg\" data-src=\"\" width=\"120px\" height=\"160px\" alt=\"斗破苍穹之倾城绝恋\">\r\n\t</a>\r\n\t<div class=\"caption\">\r\n\t\t<h4 class=\"name\">\r\n\t\t\t<a href=\"https://www.shenhuazhihou.com/book/48899/\" title=\"斗破苍穹之倾城绝恋\">斗破苍穹之倾城绝恋</a>\r\n\t\t</h4>\r\n\t\t<div class=\"author\">文武全才彬彬</div>\r\n\t\t<div class=\"intro\">三十年河东，三十年河西，莫欺少年穷我命由我不由天突破斗帝后的萧炎如何在一个新的大6上重新验证这两句话呢？萧炎吸收异火做了无数准备，而小小年纪的薰儿又为何可以掌握排名第四的金帝焚天炎呢？古元活…</div>\r\n\t</div>\r\n</div><div class=\"col-sm-6 col-md-4 book-coverlist\">\r\n\t<a class=\"cover\" href=\"https://www.shenhuazhihou.com/book/47588/\">\r\n\t\t<img class=\"thumbnail\" src=\"https://www.shenhuazhihou.com/d/file/book/de46bb3a05d0550bc773cee24c68092d.jpg\" data-src=\"\" width=\"120px\" height=\"160px\" alt=\"斗破苍穹之无上之境\">\r\n\t</a>\r\n\t<div class=\"caption\">\r\n\t\t<h4 class=\"name\">\r\n\t\t\t<a href=\"https://www.shenhuazhihou.com/book/47588/\" title=\"斗破苍穹之无上之境\">斗破苍穹之无上之境</a>\r\n\t\t</h4>\r\n\t\t<div class=\"author\">夜雨闻铃0</div>\r\n\t\t<div class=\"intro\">header分享书籍《斗破苍穹之无上之境》作者：夜雨闻铃0…</div>\r\n\t</div>\r\n</div><div class=\"col-sm-6 col-md-4 book-coverlist\">\r\n\t<a class=\"cover\" href=\"https://www.shenhuazhihou.com/book/44663/\">\r\n\t\t<img class=\"thumbnail\" src=\"https://www.shenhuazhihou.com/d/file/book/752016015612535e57ebcb790eb48ba4.jpg\" data-src=\"\" width=\"120px\" height=\"160px\" alt=\"斗破苍穹：直播问答，世界全乱了\">\r\n\t</a>\r\n\t<div class=\"caption\">\r\n\t\t<h4 class=\"name\">\r\n\t\t\t<a href=\"https://www.shenhuazhihou.com/book/44663/\" title=\"斗破苍穹：直播问答，世界全乱了\">斗破苍穹：直播问答，世界全乱了</a>\r\n\t\t</h4>\r\n\t\t<div class=\"author\">超神蛋蛋</div>\r\n\t\t<div class=\"intro\">你真的看懂了斗破苍穹？你确定你看到的就是事情的真相？你真的读懂了斗破中的每一个剧情？斗破苍穹直播问答，带你诠释真实的斗破苍穹。……直播问答若干年后【萧炎】：什么，你要和我结婚？不可能的，这辈子都不…</div>\r\n\t</div>\r\n</div><div class=\"col-sm-6 col-md-4 book-coverlist\">\r\n\t<a class=\"cover\" href=\"https://www.shenhuazhihou.com/book/doupocangqiong/\">\r\n\t\t<img class=\"thumbnail\" src=\"https://www.shenhuazhihou.com/d/file/book/c378f90ef88cb08ffca3d5d2ec727c89.jpg\" data-src=\"\" width=\"120px\" height=\"160px\" alt=\"斗破苍穹\">\r\n\t</a>\r\n\t<div class=\"caption\">\r\n\t\t<h4 class=\"name\">\r\n\t\t\t<a href=\"https://www.shenhuazhihou.com/book/doupocangqiong/\" title=\"斗破苍穹\">斗破苍穹</a>\r\n\t\t</h4>\r\n\t\t<div class=\"author\">天蚕土豆</div>\r\n\t\t<div class=\"intro\">这里是属于斗气的世界，没有花俏艳丽的魔法，有的，仅仅是繁衍到巅峰的斗气！小说人物等级制度：斗者，斗师，大斗师，斗灵，斗王，斗皇，斗宗，斗尊，斗圣，斗帝。…</div>\r\n\t</div>\r\n</div><div class=\"col-sm-6 col-md-4 book-coverlist\">\r\n\t<a class=\"cover\" href=\"https://www.shenhuazhihou.com/book/19842/\">\r\n\t\t<img class=\"thumbnail\" src=\"https://www.shenhuazhihou.com/d/file/book/c09ffb67532e392d164974bb24bbb093.jpg\" data-src=\"\" width=\"120px\" height=\"160px\" alt=\"斗破苍穹9·挺进内院\">\r\n\t</a>\r\n\t<div class=\"caption\">\r\n\t\t<h4 class=\"name\">\r\n\t\t\t<a href=\"https://www.shenhuazhihou.com/book/19842/\" title=\"斗破苍穹9·挺进内院\">斗破苍穹9·挺进内院</a>\r\n\t\t</h4>\r\n\t\t<div class=\"author\">天蚕土豆</div>\r\n\t\t<div class=\"intro\">《斗破苍穹》是起点专栏作家天蚕土豆的小说，该小说已与2011年7月20日完结。讲述的是一个属于斗气的世界，没有花俏艳丽的魔法，有的，仅仅是繁衍到巅峰的斗气！在斗气大陆上，真正的强者都是用实力说话的！《…</div>\r\n\t</div>\r\n</div><div class=\"col-sm-6 col-md-4 book-coverlist\">\r\n\t<a class=\"cover\" href=\"https://www.shenhuazhihou.com/book/19841/\">\r\n\t\t<img class=\"thumbnail\" src=\"https://www.shenhuazhihou.com/d/file/book/e89f4c29e1f8508ade8d537a0fa01f27.jpg\" data-src=\"\" width=\"120px\" height=\"160px\" alt=\"斗破苍穹10·天焚炼气塔\">\r\n\t</a>\r\n\t<div class=\"caption\">\r\n\t\t<h4 class=\"name\">\r\n\t\t\t<a href=\"https://www.shenhuazhihou.com/book/19841/\" title=\"斗破苍穹10·天焚炼气塔\">斗破苍穹10·天焚炼气塔</a>\r\n\t\t</h4>\r\n\t\t<div class=\"author\">天蚕土豆</div>\r\n\t\t<div class=\"intro\">年仅15岁的萧家废物，于此地，立下了誓言，从今以后便一步步走向斗气大陆巅峰！这里是属于斗气的世界，没有花俏艳丽的魔法，有的，仅仅是繁衍到巅峰的斗气！…</div>\r\n\t</div>\r\n</div><div class=\"col-sm-6 col-md-4 book-coverlist\">\r\n\t<a class=\"cover\" href=\"https://www.shenhuazhihou.com/book/19840/\">\r\n\t\t<img class=\"thumbnail\" src=\"https://www.shenhuazhihou.com/d/file/book/23d46f0c5b5ca58c25211c799d65c7e5.jpg\" data-src=\"\" width=\"120px\" height=\"160px\" alt=\"斗破苍穹12·陨落心炎\">\r\n\t</a>\r\n\t<div class=\"caption\">\r\n\t\t<h4 class=\"name\">\r\n\t\t\t<a href=\"https://www.shenhuazhihou.com/book/19840/\" title=\"斗破苍穹12·陨落心炎\">斗破苍穹12·陨落心炎</a>\r\n\t\t</h4>\r\n\t\t<div class=\"author\">天蚕土豆</div>\r\n\t\t<div class=\"intro\">天蚕土豆创造的这个魔幻世界是属于斗气的世界，没有花俏艳丽的魔法，有的，仅仅是繁衍到巅峰的斗气！想要知道异界的斗气在发展到巅峰之后是何种境地吗？请观斗破苍穹！苍穹诸神俱灭，斗气风云再起！天才少年萧炎…</div>\r\n\t</div>\r\n</div><div class=\"col-sm-6 col-md-4 book-coverlist\">\r\n\t<a class=\"cover\" href=\"https://www.shenhuazhihou.com/book/19839/\">\r\n\t\t<img class=\"thumbnail\" src=\"https://www.shenhuazhihou.com/d/file/book/02dc8de531e7e54869824eef4664daa1.jpg\" data-src=\"\" width=\"120px\" height=\"160px\" alt=\"斗破苍穹15·加玛风云\">\r\n\t</a>\r\n\t<div class=\"caption\">\r\n\t\t<h4 class=\"name\">\r\n\t\t\t<a href=\"https://www.shenhuazhihou.com/book/19839/\" title=\"斗破苍穹15·加玛风云\">斗破苍穹15·加玛风云</a>\r\n\t\t</h4>\r\n\t\t<div class=\"author\">天蚕土豆</div>\r\n\t\t<div class=\"intro\">天蚕土豆创造的这个魔幻世界是属于斗气的世界，没有花俏艳丽的魔法，有的，仅仅是繁衍到巅峰的斗气！想要知道异界的斗气在发展到巅峰之后是何种境地吗？请观斗破苍穹！苍穹诸神俱灭，斗气风云再起！脸色微沉地望…</div>\r\n\t</div>\r\n</div><div class=\"col-sm-6 col-md-4 book-coverlist\">\r\n\t<a class=\"cover\" href=\"https://www.shenhuazhihou.com/book/19838/\">\r\n\t\t<img class=\"thumbnail\" src=\"https://www.shenhuazhihou.com/d/file/book/4ef08391ed91d40b4ac208a81f26db1d.jpg\" data-src=\"\" width=\"120px\" height=\"160px\" alt=\"斗破苍穹13·绝处逢生\">\r\n\t</a>\